  <h2>About Cyclones</h2>
  <p>
    A cyclone is a large, rotating storm system with powerful winds and heavy rain that forms over warm ocean water.
    India‚Äôs coastal states like Odisha, West Bengal, Andhra Pradesh, Tamil Nadu, and Gujarat face frequent cyclones.
  </p>
  <p>
