<!-- PREPAREDNESS -->
<article class="content-card">
  <h2>Preparedness Before a Cyclone</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Store drinking water, dry food, medicines, and first-aid supplies.</li>
    <li>Charge mobile phones & keep power banks ready.</li>
    <li>Secure windows, doors, and unplug appliances.</li>
    <li>Keep documents in waterproof bags.</li>
    <li>Know your community‚Äôs cyclone shelters.</li>
    <li>Move livestock and vehicles to higher, safer places.</li>
  </ul>
</article>

<!-- DOs & DON'Ts -->
