  <h3>‚úî Do‚Äôs</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Stay indoors and keep emergency kit ready.</li>
    <li>Follow IMD and government instructions.</li>
    <li>Switch off electricity during severe storms.</li>
    <li>Help children, elderly, and disabled persons evacuate.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>‚ùå Don‚Äôts</h3>
  <ul>
